name: Lieutenant Commander Ardan
Lore: 'Commander of Executor bridge pit crews. Native of Brentaal. Participated in the subjugation of Ithor, Kashyyyk, Firro, Sinton and other planets populated by non-humans.',
Text: 'If at a site, draws one battle destiny if not able to otherwise. Immune to attrition < X, where X = the number of opponent''s aliens present.',
